- initial config

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
git config --global user.name "Gregorio Bueno"
git config --global user.email "garbueno@gmail.com"
git config --global core.editor subl            <<<<<------------ Subline as Editor
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- how to verify

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:~ grbueno$ git config user.name
Gregorio Bueno
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:~ grbueno$ git config user.email
garbueno@gmail.com
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:~ grbueno$ git config core.editor
subl
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- verify all

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:~ grbueno$ git config --list
credential.helper=osxkeychain
user.name=Gregorio Bueno
user.email=garbueno@gmail.com
core.editor=subl
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- create a directory and initiate Git

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ pwd
/Users/grbueno/CISCO/Git
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git init
Initialized empty Git repository in /Users/grbueno/CISCO/Git/.git/
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- Git creates a .directory under directory above

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ ls -al
total 8
drwxr-xr-x   4 grbueno  staff   136 Nov 20 12:30 ./
drwxr-xr-x  39 grbueno  staff  1326 Nov 20 12:25 ../
drwxr-xr-x   9 grbueno  staff   306 Nov 20 12:30 .git/    <<--------- Git directory
-rw-r--r--@  1 grbueno  staff   566 Nov 20 12:27 Tips     <<--------- Only file under Git monitored directory

GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ cd .git
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:.git grbueno$ ls
HEAD		config		description	hooks/		info/		objects/	refs/
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- 1st file "Tips" is Untracked (not being monitored by Git)

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status
On branch master

Initial commit

Untracked files:
  (use "git add <file>..." to include in what will be committed)

	Tips

nothing added to commit but untracked files present (use "git add" to track)
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- adding this file to Git

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git add Tips

GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status
On branch master

Initial commit

Changes to be committed:
  (use "git rm --cached <file>..." to unstage)

	new file:   Tips

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- after modifying and saving this file 'Tips', Git notes that it was modified

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status
On branch master

Initial commit

Changes to be committed:
  (use "git rm --cached <file>..." to unstage)

	new file:   Tips

Changes not staged for commit:
  (use "git add <file>..." to update what will be committed)
  (use "git checkout -- <file>..." to discard changes in working directory)

	modified:   Tips

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- adding again for commit (now it can be commited)

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git add Tips
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status
On branch master

Initial commit

Changes to be committed:
  (use "git rm --cached <file>..." to unstage)

	new file:   Tips

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- commiting a file with a comment

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git commit -m 'commit para o primeiro arquivo Tips'
[master (root-commit) d98edb5] commit para o primeiro arquivo Tips
 1 file changed, 126 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 Tips
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- after commit, there's no file on git status to be commited (all files there are already commited)

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status
On branch master
nothing to commit, working tree clean
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

== at this time, a commit was done and there's a version with last files
== git status does not return anything as the last commit is up to date.
== if we modify the file and save it, git status will return it, as the last commit is not up to date

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status
On branch master
Changes not staged for commit:
  (use "git add <file>..." to update what will be committed)
  (use "git checkout -- <file>..." to discard changes in working directory)

	modified:   Tips

no changes added to commit (use "git add" and/or "git commit -a")
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- to commit again, we need to add it for commit
- below, trying to commit without adding it for commit

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git commit -m 'commitando sem adicionar'
On branch master
Changes not staged for commit:         <<<<--------------- Files under here are not ready to be commited
	modified:   Tips

no changes added to commit
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- but if we add it for commit, and commit it:

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git add Tips             <<<<<--------------- adding for commit
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status               <<<<---------------- checking status
On branch master
Changes to be committed:                             <<<<---------------- files under here are ready to be commited
  (use "git reset HEAD <file>..." to unstage)

	modified:   Tips                                 <<<<---------------- 'Tips' can be commited

GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git commit -m 'commitando depois de adicionar'
[master 57b1c00] commitando depois de adicionar
 1 file changed, 49 insertions(+)
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

